searching over knowledge, adapting to knowledge,

01:35:04.620 --> 01:35:06.860
our molecular systems do,

01:35:06.860 --> 01:35:11.100
but the output isn't just a thought, it's us.

01:35:11.100 --> 01:35:13.060
