relatively it affects small amount of information

01:46:11.660 --> 01:46:14.020
in the genome can give rise to the complexity

01:46:14.020 --> 01:46:15.660
of who you are.

01:46:16.660 --> 01:46:21.660
That's where what resides is this molecular intelligence,

01:46:22.660 --> 01:46:24.980
which is first how to describe you,

01:46:24.980 --> 01:46:29.380
but then how to describe you such that you can exist

01:46:29.380 --> 01:46:33.580
and you can reproduce and you can grow and you can evolve.

01:46:33.580 --> 01:46:38.580
And so that's the seat of our molecular intelligence.

01:46:38.780 --> 01:46:41.100
The maker of revolution in biology.

