What advice would you give to young people?

01:52:08.860 --> 01:52:11.220
What advice have you given them?

01:52:11.220 --> 01:52:14.180
How to have one heck of a great career,

01:52:14.180 --> 01:52:15.740
one heck of a great life?

01:52:15.740 --> 01:52:20.740
What one important one is if you look at junior faculty

01:52:22.340 --> 01:52:25.460
trying to get tenure at a place like MIT,

01:52:25.460 --> 01:52:28.420
the ones who try to figure out how to get tenure

01:52:28.420 --> 01:52:30.740
