01:52:39.180 --> 01:52:42.980
and nothing else could possibly be

01:52:42.980 --> 01:52:44.500
what you wanna be doing with your life

01:52:44.500 --> 01:52:46.580
and it gets you out of bed in the morning.

01:52:46.580 --> 01:52:48.740
And again, it sounds naive,

01:52:48.740 --> 01:52:53.740
but within the limited domain I'm describing now

01:52:54.300 --> 01:52:57.340
of getting tenure at MIT, that's a key attribute to it.

01:52:57.340 --> 01:53:02.140
And in the same sense, if you take the sort of outliers

